item.title: Israel's war cabinet disbanded by Netanyahu
item.description: Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu has disbanded the country's war cabinet, an Israeli official says, just over a week after opposition leader Benny Gantz withdrew from the body. Follow for live updates.

item.title: Russian warships depart Cuba after visit following military exercises

item.description: Ann Hood, a best-selling author, has recounted her adventures working as cabin crew on TWA flights in the 1980s in a book detailing the highs and lows of life during the early jet age.

item.title: June 13, 2024 Israel-Hamas war
item.description: The US-backed Gaza ceasefire proposal doesn't meet Hamas' demands for an end to the war, a senior official has told CNN. Osama Hamdan also said that "no one has an idea" how many of the hostages held in the enclave are alive.

item.title: Chopper Cops | Paramount+ Official Trailer
item.description: The new P+ Original docuseries follows an elite team of pilots flying state-of-the-art police helicopters. These tricked-out flying machines are equipped with high-tech infrared cameras and augmented reality mapping capabilities to find armed perpetrators who are hiding. Whether it's carjackings, shooters on the run, or a family lost in the woods, failure is not an option. Stream the new docuseries on June 18th exclusively on Paramount+.

item.title: Maryland governor on why he issued mass pardon for marijuana convictions
item.description: Maryland Gov. Wes Moore pardoned more than 175,000 marijuana convictions Monday, most of which are for misdemeanors involving the possession of cannabis. Moore told CBS News' Skyler Henry the move is meant to help people of color who are disproportionally affected by criminal convictions involving marijuana.

item.title: Supreme Court maintains access to abortion pill in unanimous decision
item.description: The Supreme Court has issued a decision on whether the US Food and Drug Administration overstepped its authority by expanding access to the abortion pill mifepristone.
